title: ArkansasVarsity.com Week Seven Top 11's
text:
ArkansasVarsity.com Week Seven Top 11's Luke Matheson ArkansasVarsity.com Publisher 
We are now heading into week seven of the 2015 Arkansas high school football season, and we have seen a lot of great football played this year. This week's rankings have several shake ups, to include Class 4A, 6A, 7A, and the Natural State Top 11. 
This year ArkansasVarsity.com is teaming up with THV 11 out of Little Rock to bring you the best coverage of high school sports in the Natural state. Look for features on Arkansas high school sports each Monday and Friday on THV 11, to include rankings, predictions, thoughts on past and upcoming games and more. 
With that being said, let's get to the 2015 ArkansasVarsity.com Week Seven Football Rankings Presented by THV 11.
